  "detailed_description": "Sphaera is a game about relaxation and exploration in a huge grass field filled with animals.<br><br>You play as a small sphere, awaken as God's creation along with animals where you can collect and let them be part of yours. <br><br><strong>Key Features</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/3e5175e9404941b2afb21a3e8168bb73.poster.avif?t=1662352130\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/3e5175e9404941b2afb21a3e8168bb73.webm?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/3e5175e9404941b2afb21a3e8168bb73.mp4?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Day/Night Cycle - God said, \"Let lights appear in the sky to separate the day from the night. Let them be signs to mark the seasons, days, and years.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/4af3cad80d107accf78e2ecb945cb08f.poster.avif?t=1662352130\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/4af3cad80d107accf78e2ecb945cb08f.webm?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/4af3cad80d107accf78e2ecb945cb08f.mp4?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/47773399802ff414fb98a5d89710cd6f.poster.avif?t=1662352130\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/47773399802ff414fb98a5d89710cd6f.webm?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/47773399802ff414fb98a5d89710cd6f.mp4?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect! Collect! Collect!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/0155a1d1ec93538b19ae95546f5905e4.poster.avif?t=1662352130\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/0155a1d1ec93538b19ae95546f5905e4.webm?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/0155a1d1ec93538b19ae95546f5905e4.mp4?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Animals - Take a screenshot worthy moment with the animals. Nvidia Ansel supported.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/b85b0cefd9c0af8810688a4606694877.poster.avif?t=1662352130\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/b85b0cefd9c0af8810688a4606694877.webm?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/b85b0cefd9c0af8810688a4606694877.mp4?t=1662352130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/874270/extras/a88651de22ffb3f870c4f5a29c76f70e.avif?t=1662352130\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
